[{"type":"{{","value":[["pagebanner"],["Mena-asia_default_banner.jpg"]]},"\n",{"type":"'''","value":["Ruili"]}," (瑞丽; ",{"type":"''","value":["Ruìlì"]},") is a city in ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Yunnan"]]},", ",{"type":"[[","value":[["South West (China)"],["South-West China"]]},", on the border with ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Myanmar"]]},".\n\n",{"type":"==","value":[" Get in "]},"\nDehong Mangshi Airport (LUM), with connections to ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Kunming"]]},", is the closest airport.\n\n",{"type":"==","value":[" Get around "]},"\n\n",{"type":"==","value":[" See "]},"\n",{"type":"*","value":[" ",{"type":"'''","value":["One Tree Forest"]}]},{"type":"*","value":[" ",{"type":"'''","value":["Chinese-Burma Friendship Street"]}]},{"type":"*","value":[" ",{"type":"'''","value":["Border Trade Street"]}]},{"type":"*","value":[" ",{"type":"'''","value":["Touring and Gem Washing Field"]}]},{"type":"*","value":[" ",{"type":"'''","value":["Wanding Ecological Park"]}]},{"type":"*","value":[" ",{"type":"'''","value":["Hansa Temple"]}]},{"type":"*","value":[" ",{"type":"'''","value":["Jiele Big Golden Pagoda"]}]},"\n",{"type":"==","value":[" Do "]},"\n\n",{"type":"==","value":[" Buy "]},"\nThis town is located at the ",{"type":"[[","value":[["PRC"],["Chinese"]]},"-",{"type":"[[","value":[["Myanmar"],["Burmese"]]}," border. There is much trade in imported goods, notably jade and fabrics. Wooden furniture (sourced from Burmese logs) is also widely available. Cheap souvenirs can also be bought from travelling Burmese merchants in the city, or from the sizeable number of other foreigners present in the city such as ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Pakistan"],["Pakistanis"]]}," and ",{"type":"[[","value":[["India"],["Indians"]]},".\n\nBe prepared to ",{"type":"[[","value":[["bargain"]]}," hard. Be cautious about fake jade; see ",{"type":"[[","value":[["China#Shopping"],["discussion"]]}," in the China article.\n\n",{"type":"==","value":[" Eat "]},"\n\n",{"type":"==","value":[" Drink "]},"\n\n",{"type":"==","value":[" Sleep "]},"\nThere is a large number of hotels in Ruili. However, hotels in the city are surprisingly expensive, compared even to provincial capitals. There seem to be no places below 300 Yuan.\n",{"type":"*","value":["Jing Cheng hotel - reputed to be the best hotel in the city as well as being housed in the city's tallest tower. The city's only 4-star hotel but in reality feels more like a 2 or 3 star hotel. Breakfast provided is very limited to local cuisine."]},"\n",{"type":"==","value":[" Go next "]},"\n\n",{"type":"*","value":[" ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Mu-se"]]}," - in ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Shan State"]]},", ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Myanmar"]]}]},"\n",{"type":"[[","value":[["WikiPedia:Ruili"]]},"\n\n",{"type":"{{","value":[["geo"],["24.0167"],["97.8500"]]},"\n\n",{"type":"{{","value":[["IsPartOf"],["Western Yunnan"]]},"\n",{"type":"{{","value":[["outlinecity"]]},"\n\n",{"type":"[[","value":[["Commons:Category:Ruili City"]]}]